headline: State Street Corporation Declares Common Stock Dividend
summary: BOSTON, December 18, 2025--State Street Corporation (NYSE:STT) today announced a quarterly cash dividend of $0.84 per share of common stock, payable on January 12, 2026 to common shareholders of record at the close of business on January 2, 2026.

headline: State Street to Match U.S. Treasury Contributions to New Child Savings Accounts
summary: BOSTON, December 18, 2025--State Street Corporation (NYSE: STT) today announced a new program to match U.S. Treasury contributions to the children’s savings accounts established under the Working Family Tax Cuts initiative.
